Package: sub
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: nmap, whois, dnsutils, traceroute
Description: A powerful multi-purpose hacking and utility CLI tool
 sub is a command-line toolkit for network recon, hacking utilities,
 crypto helpers, encoding, password generation, and personal info
 display. Created by Subhobhai Sarkar (subhobhai943).
 .
 Features: nmap scan wrapper, port scanner, subdomain brute-force,
 banner grabber, DNS lookup, WHOIS, IP geolocation, ping, traceroute,
 HTTP headers, hash (MD5/SHA*), hash identifier, encode/decode
 (base64/hex/url), password/token generator, weather, GitHub repos.
